1.武将(Wu jiang),长枪(Chang qiang);官兵(Guan bing),军服(Junfu);2,媒婆(Mei_po),小红娘(Xiao hongniang)
3,大狼狗(Wolf dog),狗皮(kill dog);4,管家(Guan jia),家丁(Jia ding);5,田伯光(Tian boguang),单刀,飞沙走石十三式
(ask tian about 淫贼,accept);崔员外(Cui yuanwai),牢房钥匙;崔莺莺(Cui yingying);6,林平之(Lin pingzhi),镖头(Biao tou)
7,林震南(Lin zhennan)(练辟邪剑法与之有关,ask about 福威镖局,远图公,辟邪剑法);8,流氓(Liu mang) 流氓头(Liumang tou)
9,衙役(Ya yi),衙役服(Yayi cloth);谭友纪(Tan youji),程药发(Cheng yaofa;程玉环(Cheng yuhuan),金项链(Golden necklace)
